      "writtenOn": "2026-04-17T07:20:23Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Good point. I did a search and it seems that INI commonly just treats all values simply as strings. I\u0027ve added another config options for \"TypedValues\", which defaults to \"false\" and the values will all be just treated as strings by default.",
      "parentUuid": "90eb887b_15c84ac7",
